  "detailed_description": "Ash Battle is a Sci-Fi minimalist survival game with a Bullet Hell style.<br>Ash is on an unknown planet and has found many enemies who didn't like his visit. Prepare yourself and be ready for battle, because they come in huge numbers.<br><br><strong>Goals</strong>:<br>Try to survive the large amount of enemies, they will chase you wherever you go. You will not be able to escape them.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2110320/extras/2ee09750bca21da51f0f7d704adc35f4.avif?t=1696954464\" width=600 height=300 /></span><br><br><strong>Weapons</strong><br>Use your sword and your weapon to fight your enemies, each of them has a special ability that you can take advantages<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2110320/extras/a3e78811ee91605d6f216414d40f2014.avif?t=1696954464\" width=600 height=300 /></span><br><br><strong>Map</strong><br>Use a map to navigate and evade your enemies if you can!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2110320/extras/1e438c4773674c93a1201afb0f81b45d.avif?t=1696954464\" width=600 height=300 /></span><br><br><strong>Rank</strong><br>Get points with each game and try to overcome your limits.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2110320/extras/b42b8fae60566ee72815c709170f8794.avif?t=1696954464\" width=600 height=300 /></span><br><br><strong>Boss</strong><br>Face the most powerful enemy on this inhospitable planet and try to defeat him.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2110320/extras/4a28d3815d4e8c1c1248ef838214f5ad.avif?t=1696954464\" width=600 height=300 /></span>",
  "about_the_game": "Ash Battle is a Sci-Fi minimalist survival game with a Bullet Hell style.<br>Ash is on an unknown planet and has found many enemies who didn't like his visit. Prepare yourself and be ready for battle, because they come in huge numbers.<br><br><strong>Goals</strong>:<br>Try to survive the large amount of enemies, they will chase you wherever you go. You will not be able to escape them.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2110320/extras/2ee09750bca21da51f0f7d704adc35f4.avif?t=1696954464\" width=600 height=300 /></span><br><br><strong>Weapons</strong><br>Use your sword and your weapon to fight your enemies, each of them has a special ability that you can take advantages<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2110320/extras/a3e78811ee91605d6f216414d40f2014.avif?t=1696954464\" width=600 height=300 /></span><br><br><strong>Map</strong><br>Use a map to navigate and evade your enemies if you can!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2110320/extras/1e438c4773674c93a1201afb0f81b45d.avif?t=1696954464\" width=600 height=300 /></span><br><br><strong>Rank</strong><br>Get points with each game and try to overcome your limits.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2110320/extras/b42b8fae60566ee72815c709170f8794.avif?t=1696954464\" width=600 height=300 /></span><br><br><strong>Boss</strong><br>Face the most powerful enemy on this inhospitable planet and try to defeat him.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2110320/extras/4a28d3815d4e8c1c1248ef838214f5ad.avif?t=1696954464\" width=600 height=300 /></span>",
